quences, which suggest similarities between DLAs and nearby\ngalaxies. We suggest that the transition-mass model provides a plausible\nscenario for the bimodality we have found. As a result, the bimodality in\ncurrent galaxies may have originated in DLAs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Feb 2008 21:32:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
